From 06defb47b718d1c997941f39ee9daad56665f42f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: lutong <lutong14@huawei.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 22:37:33 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] fs/hugetlbfs: add file-backed HugeTLB page swap and
 swapoff support

Extend hugetlb swap to file-backed hugetlbfs mappings: pages can be
written to swap with their slot recorded as an XArray value entry in
the page cache, and faulted back in transparently. Implement swapoff
support for hugetlb pages, including hugetlbfs_unuse() to read back
swapped-out pages during swapoff.

Signed-off-by: nashzhou <zhouhaipeng13@huawei.com>
